ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A good theoretical and practical overviews of the major issues in terrorism and CT.
Absolutely; great opportunity to learn from someone who's worked on these issues at the highest levels.
Highly recommend. Great course, I hope she teaches it again.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course helped shaped my thinking about senior thesis topics; Professor Malvesti has been very helpful in that regard.
This was a great class, it really helped me see terrorism through something other than "the Al Qaeda lens."
